            &lt;artifactId&gt;core&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;12.62.7&lt;/version&gt;
         &lt;/dependency&gt;

Add the following in module-info.java file:                 
                                                                             
     requires org.burningwave.core;

